account_creates_list = query_account_creates()

## account_upgrades

## save data
last_query_block = account_creates_list[-1]['created_at_block'] - 1
with open(f'data/account_creates_up_to_block_{last_query_block}.json', 'w') as f:
    json.dump({"account_creates":account_creates_list}, f)

with open(f'data/account_upgrades_up_to_block_{last_query_block}.json', 'w') as f:
    json.dump({"account_creates":account_upgrades_list}, f)
